  "commentary": "**DEALER HEDGING COMMENTARY:**\n\nWith SPX at 6797.69 sitting between the negative gamma pocket at 6755 (-1900.7M) and the massive positive gamma wall at 6850-6900 (+3200M to +4700M), dealers are currently in buy-the-dip mode as we're below the 6896 flip strike in PIN regime. The 31.9% GEX surge suggests options flow is creating stronger magnetic effects around these key levels, with dealers likely stepping in as buyers on this pullback toward the 6755 amplifying zone. Expect strong resistance into the 6850-6900 zone where dealers will aggressively sell rallies, while 6755 represents critical support where dealer buying should accelerate if tested.\n\n**Bottom line:** Price should bounce between 6755 support and 6850-6900 resistance with dealers providing stabilizing flows.",
